newsitem.title: ARGENTINA: Argentine Central Bank places $260 mln repos.
newsitem.headline: Argentine Central Bank places $260 mln repos.

text.p: Argentina's Central Bank said Tuesday it placed $260 million in overnight repurchase agreements at nine percent.
In the interbank market, call money rose to 8.6 percent from 8.3 percent at the close Friday.
The U.S. dollar rose to 0.99995 pesos from 0.99942 pesos Friday.
